---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Me">
  <div class="container container__home">
    <h1 class="main-heading">HI Again!</h1>
    <p class="heyjoe_paragraph">
      I'm someone who's driven by growth, grit, and exploration, both in work and in life. I'm a
      lifelong learner who taught myself front-end development and product design out of curiosity and
      a love for building simple, intuitive experiences from complex problems.
    </p>
    <p class="heyjoe_paragraph">
      Outside of work, endurance is part of my identity: I've run marathons and ultras, helped raise
      my younger brother with a lot of love and responsibility, and learned to treat hard things as
      chances to evolve.
    </p>
    <p class="heyjoe_paragraph">
      Lately, I've been bringing that same mindset into my day-to-day work by integrating AI
      workflows into discovery, research, and prototype building; moving faster, iterating more, and
      staying close to the problem.
    </p>
    <p class="heyjoe_paragraph">
      Whether I'm deep in a book, building products, or hiking on a "forest bathing" adventure, I
      seek experiences that sharpen my thinking and keep me grounded. I'll take nature over city
      noise, and complexity over the easy path. I believe the best journeys—professionally and
      personally—are the ones shaped by leaning into challenge and pushing past comfort.
    </p>
    <img
      src="/images/og_jonathan_beltran_senior_product_designer.jpg"
      loading="lazy"
      alt="Jonathan Beltrán, Senior Product Designer"
      class="portfolio-img img-internal img-internal-with-caption"
      style="width: 100%; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 35px;"
    />
    <h2 class="main-heading">let's connect</h2>
    <div class="fond-me-wrapper">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/heyjoe/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hj-button"
        >LinkedIn</a
      >
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/heyjoeb/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hj-button"
        >IG</a
      >
      <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/heyjoeb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hj-button"
        >GoodReads</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
